<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />新年很多人都会去抽签，<delay20 />
不过<delay8 />就算抽到“凶”，
也不必太难过！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要小心签上写着的注意事项，<delay8 />
运气就不会继续变差啦。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />倒不如说一整年运气都会提升啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00">零花钱啊<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已经<delay8 />好久没有拿到过啦。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说起来，<delay8 />小时候拿到零花钱之后，<delay20 />
老妈说“我替你保管”就把零花钱拿走了，<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好像到现在都还在保管中啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说到新年就会想到年糕汤啊！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过<delay8 />同样是年糕汤，<delay8 />
也有许多<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不同的吃法啊。
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我比较喜欢在白味增汤中，
放入没有烤过的年糕。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这样年糕吃起来比较软！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay20 />
你今年<delay8 />有没有什么<delay8 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />目标或者抱负之类的啊？
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我啊<tag a="110" b="0" />
<colour id="4" />希望今年腰痛能够远离我<tag a="110" b="0" /><colour id="65535" /><pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊～<delay8 />
感觉一旦说出口愿望就无法成真了，<delay20 />
所以还是不谈这个了吧。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />人们常说新年第一场梦里出现<delay20 />
“一富士、<delay8 />二鹰、<delay8 />三茄子”，<delay8 />
就是吉祥的象征。<pageBreak />那把它改成一富士、<delay8 />二<tag a="110" b="15" /><delay8 />、三<tag a="110" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />，<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你觉得怎么样？<pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />什么？<delay8 />你说不顺口不好念？<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那当然咯，<delay8 />因为我刚才说的时候
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也差点咬到舌头啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>